    <h1>Your Rights During Police &amp; ICE Encounters</h1>
    <p class="lede">If you are stopped by law enforcement or by Immigration and Customs Enforcement, the most important thing to understand is that you have rights — and using those rights does not mean you have done anything wrong.</p>
    <p class="updated">Updated as of April 30, 2026</p>
  </div>
</section>

